name: Shadow Jets Paper plane Survival
description: Shadow jet paper shooter! Doodle Jump meets Space Invaders. Cool shadow jet fighting game where you must dodge and shoot the enemy doodle army. Classic game play with a really cool stickman or doodle drawing art style a kid would draw in school. Its like daydreaming in class while the teacher is talking about your drawings coming to life. Really fun and simple. Good game for kids, boys, and a good game for girls as well. Have Fun!!
